bit,
in,
dir,
width,

xstep,
xmod,
err,
S   ) 
 

Value:

do                                                                      \
{                                                                       \
  int ii;                                                               \
  int jj;                                                               \
  for (ii = 0; ii < width; ii++)                                        \
    for (jj = 0; jj < S; jj++)                                          \
      err[ii][jj] += dir;                                               \
  if (dir == 1)                                                         \
    ADVANCE_UNIDIRECTIONAL(d, bit, in, width, xer, xstep, xmod);        \
  else                                                                  \
    ADVANCE_REVERSE(d, bit, in, width, xer, xstep, xmod);               \
} while (0)

bit,

Value:

do                                                                      \
{                                                                       \
  if (bit == 128)                                                       \
    {                                                                   \
      d->ptr_offset--;                                                  \
      bit = 1;                                                          \
    }                                                                   \
  else                                                                  \
    bit <<= 1;                                                          \
  input -= xstep;                                                       \
  if (xmod)                                                             \
    {                                                                   \
      xerror -= xmod;                                                   \
      if (xerror < 0)                                                   \
        {                                                               \
          xerror += d->dst_width;                                       \
          input -= (width);                                             \
        }                                                               \
    }                                                                   \
} while (0)
